=== microGPT Architecture Summary (Reference)

[cols="3,2,2,3",options="header"]
|===
|Component |Input |Output |Parameters

|Token Embedding |`[T]` ints |stem:[[T \times d\]] |stem:[|V| \times d]
|Positional Embedding |`[T]` positions |stem:[[T \times d\]] |stem:[T_{max} \times d]
|× N Transformer Blocks | | |
|— LayerNorm 1 |stem:[[T \times d\]] |stem:[[T \times d\]] |`2d`
|— Multi-Head Attn |stem:[[T \times d\]] |stem:[[T \times d\]] |stem:[4d^2]
|— Residual |stem:[[T \times d\]] |stem:[[T \times d\]] |0
|— LayerNorm 2 |stem:[[T \times d\]] |stem:[[T \times d\]] |`2d`
|— FFN |stem:[[T \times d\]] |stem:[[T \times d\]] |stem:[8d^2]
|— Residual |stem:[[T \times d\]] |stem:[[T \times d\]] |0
|Final LayerNorm |stem:[[T \times d\]] |stem:[[T \times d\]] |`2d`
|Unembedding |`[d]` |stem:[[|V|\]] |stem:[d \times |V|] (tied)
|===

*Total parameters:* stem:[2|V|d + T_{max}\cdot d + N(12d^2 + 4d) + 2d]

For GPT-2 small: `d=768, N=12, |V|=50257, T_max=1024` → ~117M params.
